      <div class="movement-card"><div class="mi">🤜</div><h4>Pulling</h4><p>Rows, pull-ups, opening doors</p></div>
      <div class="movement-card"><div class="mi">🔄</div><h4>Rotational</h4><p>Torso rotation, throwing, golf, dance</p></div>
